blake2bjava

Class Blake2b

  • java.lang.Object
    • blake2bjava.Blake2b

  • public class Blake2b
extends java.lang.Object
    Blake2b hash. Implementation of Blake2b hash algorithm. This class exposes interfaces to generate digest for a given message. Default digest size is 64 bit.
    Author:
    Soon Hyung Kwon, Andre Hashimoto Oku
